    Program ........ Remote Console Utility Plugin for Cacti
    Version ........ 0.1
    Purpose ........ Connect to a host using either SSH or Telnet

*******************************************************************************/


----[ Purpose

    This plugin is designed to be a utility plugin for other plugins that provides
    both Telnet and SSH access for remote hosts.

----[ Features

    Allows specification of background color, foreground color, font size, window
    size.  It provides two hooks to include in your plugin for providing a link
    and an action icon.

----[ Installation

    Install just like any other plugin from Plugin Management

----[ Possible Bugs?
   
    If you find a problem, please goto the Cacti Forums for additional support

----[ Future Changes
    
    No plans

----[ Changelog

    --- 0.1 ---
    Initial release
     
